      <title>据称，阿波罗支持的 OLB 将在 4 月 IPO 中寻求 20 亿美元的估值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/apollo-backed-olb-said-to-seek-2-billion-valuation-in-april-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，德国奥尔登堡州银行 (Oldenburgische Landesbank AG) 正在筹备首次公开募股 (IPO)。两年前，这家私募股权控股的德国地方银行搁置了早先的上市计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/apollo-backed-olb-said-to-seek-2-billion-valuation-in-april-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 16:09:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔表示仍不急于降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/fed-s-powell-says-still-no-hurry-to-lower-interest-rates-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔再次暗示官员们将耐心等待进一步降低借贷成本，称央行无需急于调整利率。鲍威尔周二在参议院银行和住房委员会就半年度货币政策报告向国会作证时发表了上述讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/fed-s-powell-says-still-no-hurry-to-lower-interest-rates-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 16:09:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔承诺以“新视角”审视银行去中心化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/fed-s-powell-commits-to-taking-fresh-look-at-debanking-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在参议院银行委员会作证时表示，美联储将致力于结束银行去中心化政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/fed-s-powell-commits-to-taking-fresh-look-at-debanking-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 16:07:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍威尔称国库支付系统是安全的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/powell-says-treasury-payment-system-is-safe-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在参议院银行委员会作证时表示，美联储仅充当财政部的财政代理，代表其处理联邦支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/powell-says-treasury-payment-system-is-safe-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 15:59:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯法院威胁后，联合信贷银行放弃英国诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/unicredit-backs-down-from-uk-lawsuit-after-russian-court-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在俄罗斯法院威胁对这家意大利银行处以 2.5 亿欧元（2.58 亿美元）的罚款后，意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 将停止对俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司 (Gazprom PJSC) 合资企业的英国高额诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/unicredit-backs-down-from-uk-lawsuit-after-russian-court-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 15:55:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国石油公司首席执行官表示，这家石油巨头的重大重组已进行了一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/bp-ceo-says-oil-major-s-big-reset-has-been-a-year-in-making</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司首席执行官 Murray Auchincloss 坚称，公司的“根本性调整”已经筹备了一年，同时拒绝对分析师关于他是否与激进投资者 Elliott Investment Management 有过接触的问题发表评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/bp-ceo-says-oil-major-s-big-reset-has-been-a-year-in-making</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 15:49:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔：向参议院银行委员会发表完整声明</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/fed-s-powell-full-statement-to-senate-banking-committee-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，“鉴于我们的政策立场现在比以前宽松得多，且经济保持强劲，我们无需急于调整政策立场。”鲍威尔周二在参议院银行和住房委员会就半年度货币政策报告向国会作证时发表了上述言论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/fed-s-powell-full-statement-to-senate-banking-committee-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 15:48:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛放弃 IPO 多元化承诺，因美国 DEI 目标受到质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/goldman-kills-ipo-diversity-pledge-with-us-dei-goals-under-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 正在放弃一项重要承诺，即拒绝与董事会全部为白人男性的公司开展首次公开募股业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/goldman-kills-ipo-diversity-pledge-with-us-dei-goals-under-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 14:36:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其在长达十年的中断后恢复购买美国债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/turkey-returns-to-buying-us-treasuries-after-dumping-75-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，土耳其近十年来首次开始购买美国国债，标志着土耳其自 2016 年中美紧张局势加剧以来减持美国国债的趋势结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/turkey-returns-to-buying-us-treasuries-after-dumping-75-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 14:09:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券收益率因鲍威尔的观望信号而上升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔重申央行不急于降息，导致国债收益率上升，股市波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 22:22:49 GMT</pubDate>
